OL,3,CHigh Court trial against Gerry Adams
OL,4,Cset to begin
OL,6,FA civil trial between three men
OL,7,Finjured in Provisional IRA bombings
OL,8,Fand Gerry Adams is set to begin at the
OL,9,FHigh Court on Monday.
OL,11,FJohn Clark, a victim of the 1973 Old
OL,12,FBailey bombing in London, Jonathan
OL,13,FGanesh, a 1996 London Docklands
OL,14,Fbombing victim, and Barry Laycock, a
OL,15,Fvictim of the 1996 Arndale shopping
OL,16,Fcentre bombing in Manchester, all
OL,17,Fallege that Mr Adams was a leading
OL,18,Fmember of the Provisional IRA on those
OL,19,Fdates, including of its Army Council.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
