OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773034803
OL,3,CHigh Court trial against Gerry Adams
OL,4,Cset to begin
OL,6,FThe trio are bringing legal action
OL,7,Fagainst the former Sinn Fein president
OL,8,Fand are seeking just #1 in damages.
OL,10,FThey claim Mr Adams "acted together
OL,11,Fwith others in furtherance of a common
OL,12,Fdesign to bomb the British mainland"
OL,13,Fand was "directly responsible" in
OL,14,Fvarious roles within the Provisional
OL,15,FIRA for decisions made to place
OL,16,Fdevices in 1973 and 1996.
OL,18,FMr Adams denies that he had any role
OL,19,Fin the Provisional IRA and is opposing
OL,20,Fthe claim.
OL,26,@rD@UOUtD@dO]uD@IOUuD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
