OL,3,CHigh Court trial against Gerry Adams
OL,4,Cset to begin
OL,6,FThe trial before Mr Justice Swift, due
OL,7,Fto begin at 10.30am on Monday at the
OL,8,FRoyal Courts of Justice in London, is
OL,9,Fexpected to last seven days.
OL,11,FLawyers for the three bombing victims
OL,12,Ftold a previous hearing that Mr Adams
OL,13,Fshould be considered a representative
OL,14,Fof a class of people who "were members
OL,15,Fof the Provisional IRA/its Army
OL,16,FCouncil between 1973 and 1996".
OL,18,FThe men also wanted to sue the
OL,19,FProvisional IRA but Mr Justice Soole
OL,20,Fsaid that claim must be struck out
OL,21,Fbecause it is "not a legal entity".
OL,26,@vD@ZOUxD@^O]}D@OOU}D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
