OL,3,CHigh Court trial against Gerry Adams
OL,4,Cset to begin
OL,6,FTwo of the witnesses due to give
OL,7,Fevidence against Mr Adams will be
OL,8,Fanonymous and will speak at the trial
OL,9,Ffrom behind a screen.
OL,11,FAnne Studd KC, for the three men, told
OL,12,Fa hearing last month that one of the
OL,13,Fwitnesses believes "the Provisional
OL,14,FIRA or people associated with it still
OL,15,Fexist" and will be in danger as a
OL,16,Fresult.
OL,18,FShe said: "This case is very likely to
OL,19,Fincrease interest again in these
OL,20,Fissues and this witness, with his past
OL,21,Fexperience, is concerned about that."
OL,26,@uD@TOUwD@FO]zD@KOU}D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
